  "title": "tiledMapBinding",
  "description": "Declarative asset binding for TiledMap. Token-only: `loader.load(TiledMap, 'world.tmj')` resolves through this binding, but no `extensions` are claimed, so a plain `loader.load('world.tmj')` does not resolve to `TiledMap`. The `.tmj` extension (and generic `.json` Tiled loading) is reserved for the format-independent `TileMap` runtime asset binding.",
